Leo G. Carroll https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Leo_G._Carroll 0 Leo Gratten Carroll (25 October 1886 – 16 October 1972) was an English actor. He was best known for his roles in several Hitchcock films, and in three television series, Topper, Going My Way, and The Man from U.N.C.L.E..
